: "$13.05", "bbox": [980.2, 704.9, 1037.5, 725.8]}, {"text": "Nonvested balance at December 31, 2015 . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [225.0, 738.3, 814.9, 759.1]}, {"text": "2,576,504", "bbox": [853.1, 738.3, 936.5, 759.1]}, {"text": "$12.95", "bbox": [980.2, 738.3, 1037.5, 759.1]}, {"text": "Intrinsic value for stock options is calculated based on the exercise price of the underlying awards and the", "bbox": [225.0, 800.8, 1109.0, 821.6]}, {"text": "quoted price of Verisk’s common stock as of the reporting date. The aggregate intrinsic value of stock options", "bbox": [162.5, 825.8, 1081.8, 846.6]}, {"text": "outstanding and exercisable at December 31, 2015 was $334,691 and $307,924, respectively. In accordance with", "bbox": [162.5, 850.8, 1103.8, 871.6]}, {"text": "ASC 718, excess tax benefit from exercised stock options is recorded as an increase to additional-paid-in capital", "bbox": [162.5, 875.8, 1099.7, 896.6]}, {"text": "and a corresponding reduction in taxes payable. This tax benefit is calculated as the excess of the intrinsic value", "bbox": [162.5, 900.8, 1096.4, 921.6]}, {"text": "of options exercised in excess of compensation recognized for financial reporting purposes. The amount of the", "bbox": [162.5, 925.8, 1085.3, 946.6]}, {"text": "tax benefit that has been realized, as a result of those excess tax benefits, is presented as a financing cash inflow", "bbox": [162.5, 950.8, 1097.0, 971.6]}, {"text": "within the accompanying consolidated statements of cash flows. For the years ended December 31, 2015, 2014", "bbox": [162.5, 975.8, 1089.6, 996.6]}, {"text": "and 2013, the Company recorded excess tax benefit from exercised stock options of $29,230, $15,988 and", "bbox": [162.5, 1000.8, 1048.3, 1021.6]}, {"text": "$58,056, respectively. The Company realized $40,147, $22,566 and $109,946 of tax benefit within the", "bbox": [162.5, 1025.8, 1017.4, 1046.6]}, {"text": "Company’s tax payments through December 31, 2015, 2014 and 2013, respectively. The Company estimates", "bbox": [162.5, 1050.8, 1071.2, 1071.6]}, {"text": "expected forfeitures of equity awards at the date of grant and recognizes compensation expense only for those", "bbox": [162.5, 1075.8, 1079.4, 1096.6]}, {"text": "awards that the Company expects to vest. The forfeiture assumption is ultimately adjusted to the actual forfeiture", "bbox": [162.5, 1100.8, 1105.7, 1121.6]}, {"text": "rate. Changes in the forfeiture assumptions may impact the total amount of expense ultimately recognized over", "bbox": [162.5, 1125.8, 1089.0, 1146.6]}, {"text": "the requisite service period and may impact the timing of expense recognized over the requisite service period.", "bbox": [162.5, 1150.8, 1087.2, 1171.6]}, {"text": "Stock based compensation expense for 2015, 2014 and 2013 was $30,542, $20,253 and $21,087, respectively.", "bbox": [162.5, 1175.8, 1080.1, 1196.6]}, {"text": "96", "bbox": [627.1, 1484.1, 647.9, 1504.9]}]}